          "description": "The eigencluster reached its absolute zenith (+13%) with the release of Born to Die, becoming the defining aesthetic of the year for Tumblr culture and alternative pop. The saturation was total; the imagery of the 'gangster Nancy Sinatra' sitting on a throne flanked by tigers created a high-density gravitation well that warped the trajectories of other pop stars. The variance was driven by the album's aggressive doubling down on Americana tropes—The National Anthem video explicitly reenacting the Kennedy assassination. This was the peak of the 'constructed self'; the distance between the artist and the myth was non-existent. The 'catalyst' was the sheer budget and cinematic scope of the music videos, which operated more like short films.",
